---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - Empire Inc"
  description="Privacy Policy for Empire Inc mobile application"
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-slate-950 text-white py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy for Empire Inc</h1>
      
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8">
        <strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 7, 2026
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            Welcome to Empire Inc ("we," "our," or "us"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application ("App").
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">2.1 Information You Provide</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Email address, username, and password when you create an account</li>
            <li><strong>Profile Information:</strong> Display name, avatar preferences</li>
            <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Processed securely through Apple App Store/Google Play Store</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">2.2 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system, unique device identifiers</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Game progress, in-app actions, session duration</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics Data:</strong> App performance, crash reports, feature usage</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">2.3 Third-Party Services</h3>
          <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Supabase:</strong> Database and authentication</li>
            <li><strong>RevenueCat:</strong> Subscription management</li>
            <li><strong>Google AdMob:</strong> Advertising (for non-premium users)</li>
            <li><strong>Sentry:</strong> Error tracking and performance monitoring</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use your information to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Provide and maintain the App</li>
            <li>Process transactions and manage subscriptions</li>
            <li>Personalize your gaming experience</li>
            <li>Send game notifications and updates</li>
            <li>Improve our services and develop new features</li>
            <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Information Sharing</h2>
          <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Third-party companies that help us operate the App</li>
            <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect our rights</li>
            <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In connection with a merger or acquisition</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Data Security</h2>
          <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information, including:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Encryption of data in transit and at rest</li>
            <li>Secure authentication mechanisms</li>
            <li>Regular security audits</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Delete your account and data</li>
            <li>Export your data</li>
            <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Empire Inc is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">8. Advertising</h2>
          <p>
            Non-premium users may see advertisements. You can remove ads by subscribing to our premium plans.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">9. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We retain your data as long as your account is active. You can request deletion by contacting us.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy. We will notify you of significant changes through the App.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">11. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>For questions about this Privacy Policy:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@empireinc.app" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">privacy@empireinc.app</a></li>
            <li>Website: <a href="https://empireinc.app" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">https://empireinc.app</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800">
        <p class="text-slate-400">Empire Inc</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

